title: Josipa Lisac - Dnevnik Jedne Ljubavi (1973)
description:
Josipa Lisac - Dnevnik jedne ljubavi (1973)


  
COVERS (front, back)


Dnevnik jedne ljubavi (Diary of a Love) is the debut album by Yuoslav singer 

Josipa Lisac, released by Jugoton in 1973.

Dnevnik jedne ljubavi is one of the best concept albums of Yugoslav pop rock 

and is considered a classic.

The album was polled in 1998 as the ninth on the list of 100 greatest 

Yugoslav rock and pop albums in the book YU 100: najbolji albumi 

jugoslovenske rok i pop muzike (YU 100: The Best albums of Yugoslav pop and 

rock music).
